293
00:16:33,426 --> 00:16:35,661
Yes. I'm sorry.

294
00:16:37,057 --> 00:16:38,498
I hope you'll treat me to it

295
00:16:38,523 --> 00:16:39,365
next year too.

296
00:16:39,391 --> 00:16:40,733
Got it.

297
00:16:40,906 --> 00:16:42,301
I got it!

298
00:17:03,249 --> 00:17:04,290
Alright.

299
00:17:04,670 --> 00:17:05,892
It's time to go home.

300
00:17:06,157 --> 00:17:06,893
Yes.

301
00:17:08,853 --> 00:17:09,944
Shall we have a BBQ

302
00:17:09,960 --> 00:17:11,272
in the backyard for dinner?

303
00:17:11,296 --> 00:17:12,298
That sounds great.

304
00:17:13,983 --> 00:17:15,234
The sea!

305
00:17:21,564 --> 00:17:22,441
Come on.

306
00:17:22,503 --> 00:17:24,168
Let's hurry up and do some shopping.

307
00:17:29,676 --> 00:17:30,816
Alright.

308
00:17:31,144 --> 00:17:32,488
First, let's get some meat.

309
00:17:39,351 --> 00:17:40,393
Minato-san,

310
00:17:40,979 --> 00:17:42,228
what was that earlier?

311
00:17:43,201 --> 00:17:44,001
Huh?

312
00:17:44,228 --> 00:17:45,530
If it was embarrassing for you,

313
00:17:45,555 --> 00:17:46,675
I'll accept it.

314
00:17:47,133 --> 00:17:48,601
But in your case,

315
00:17:48,922 --> 00:17:51,037
that wasn't the only reason, right?

316
00:17:52,939 --> 00:17:54,540
Do you still feel guilty

317
00:17:54,564 --> 00:17:56,776
about being in a relationship with me?

318
00:17:57,610 --> 00:17:59,512
No, it's not like I just...

319
00:18:03,282 --> 00:18:04,951
I'm already a university student,

320
00:18:05,567 --> 00:18:07,019
even the law allows it.

321
00:18:10,019 --> 00:18:11,457
But you still...

322
00:18:13,353 --> 00:18:15,394
need acknowledgment
from whom or what?

323
00:18:17,830 --> 00:18:18,965
You

324
00:18:19,424 --> 00:18:21,807
don't understand my feelings at all.

325
00:18:25,118 --> 00:18:26,939
Do you really love me?

326
00:18:27,181 --> 00:18:29,675
I chose to be with you...

327
00:18:30,066 --> 00:18:31,911
Isn't that enough to understand?

328
00:18:32,778 --> 00:18:33,824
Stop making a fuss.

329
00:18:33,841 --> 00:18:35,521
Let's do the shopping already.

330
00:18:47,360 --> 00:18:48,361
Hey, Shin.

331
00:18:48,751 --> 00:18:49,883
It's grilled perfectly.

332
00:18:53,711 --> 00:18:54,800
Come on. Eat.

333
00:19:02,742 --> 00:19:04,276
Ahhh...

334
00:19:08,907 --> 00:19:09,849
How is it?

335
00:19:13,586 --> 00:19:14,720
It's delicious.

336
00:19:14,931 --> 00:19:16,022
Right?

337
00:19:16,381 --> 00:19:17,423
I'm glad.

338
00:19:24,823 --> 00:19:26,632
What is it?

339
00:19:26,656 --> 00:19:28,701
Why are you sighing like that?

340
00:19:32,004 --> 00:19:32,838
Sometimes...

341
00:19:34,473 --> 00:19:35,474
My feelings...

342
00:19:36,208 --> 00:19:38,811
for you sometimes become overwhelming,

343
00:19:40,012 --> 00:19:42,615
I can't help but wonder if being

344
00:19:43,248 --> 00:19:44,660
in a relationship with you

345
00:19:44,685 --> 00:19:46,045
is only a dream.

346
00:19:46,852 --> 00:19:48,154
What are you talking about?

347
00:19:52,326 --> 00:19:53,866
It's not a dream, right?

348
00:19:55,155 --> 00:19:56,123
Hey.

349
00:19:59,826 --> 00:20:02,001
Why are you pinching my cheek?

350
00:20:13,566 --> 00:20:15,915
I acted a bit awkward earlier,

351
00:20:16,251 --> 00:20:17,516
I'm sorry.

352
00:20:18,487 --> 00:20:19,221
Huh?

353
00:20:20,979 --> 00:20:23,022
You let go of your hand,

354
00:20:23,100 --> 00:20:24,657
you were conscious of others watching.

355
00:20:25,624 --> 00:20:26,862
Even though I want to

356
00:20:26,887 --> 00:20:28,567
touch you all the time.

357
00:20:29,137 --> 00:20:30,711
That was not always the case for you.

358
00:20:31,643 --> 00:20:33,479
It depends on the time and situation.

359
00:20:35,937 --> 00:20:36,838
Sometimes.

360
00:20:38,823 --> 00:20:41,950
I can't understand
Minato-san's thoughts...

361
00:20:46,636 --> 00:20:48,013
Because we're different

362
00:20:49,115 --> 00:20:50,750
so the attraction is stronger.

363
00:20:55,821 --> 00:20:57,690
I have my own thoughts,

364
00:20:58,978 --> 00:21:01,260
and you have your own.

365
00:21:03,829 --> 00:21:04,997
That's why...

366
00:21:06,165 --> 00:21:08,000
I love Minato-san.

367
00:21:13,739 --> 00:21:14,707
Shin...

368
00:21:18,544 --> 00:21:20,212
You're different from me,

369
00:21:21,914 --> 00:21:22,848
so...

370
00:21:24,683 --> 00:21:26,752
we can at least share a bedroom.

371
00:21:26,909 --> 00:21:27,820
Yeah.

372
00:21:28,476 --> 00:21:29,555
Alright then.

373
00:21:32,531 --> 00:21:34,326
As if that is okay!

374
00:21:34,693 --> 00:21:36,235
No sharing a bedroom!

375
00:21:38,722 --> 00:21:39,833
Seriously,

376
00:21:39,857 --> 00:21:41,546
I can never let my guard down

377
00:21:41,571 --> 00:21:42,571
around you.

378
00:21:43,669 --> 00:21:45,070
If you keep saying that.

379
00:21:45,481 --> 00:21:47,139
I won't grill meat for you.

380
00:21:48,240 --> 00:21:49,308
Minato-san.

381
00:21:49,488 --> 00:21:50,910
Please grill the meat for me.

382
00:21:51,334 --> 00:21:52,678
I'm sorry.

383
00:21:53,577 --> 00:21:54,814
Sure.

384
00:21:55,010 --> 00:21:56,848
It's good that you're being honest.

385
00:21:57,703 --> 00:21:58,584
Alright.

386
00:21:59,982 --> 00:22:02,236
Hey, they're all burned!

387
00:22:02,260 --> 00:22:03,322
Ah, I'm sorry!

388
00:22:03,450 --> 00:22:04,623
Go grab a plate.

389
00:22:12,125 --> 00:22:13,766
- I'm off.
- Yeah.

390
00:22:13,899 --> 00:22:14,834
Have a safe trip.

391
00:22:19,931 --> 00:22:21,440
Minato-san, I forgot something.

392
00:22:25,167 --> 00:22:26,802
Just like newlyweds!

393
00:22:27,847 --> 00:22:30,115
We're not newlyweds!

394
00:22:30,783 --> 00:22:32,139
Hurry up and leave!

395
00:22:39,158 --> 00:22:40,259
I'm leaving.

396
00:22:50,419 --> 00:22:51,837
You okay? Anxious?

397
00:22:51,861 --> 00:22:52,838
I'm anxious.

398
00:22:52,862 --> 00:22:54,862
It's fine. Don't worry.

399
00:23:04,489 --> 00:23:05,417
It's okay.

400
00:23:09,469 --> 00:23:10,522
What is it?

401
00:23:13,797 --> 00:23:14,793
We are

402
00:23:14,864 --> 00:23:16,295
