- Yes.

405
00:23:27,627 --> 00:23:29,475
Minato Shouji Coin Laundry.

406
00:23:29,607 --> 00:23:30,978
A summer storm is approaching.

407
00:23:31,003 --> 00:23:32,017
Please be cautious.

408
00:23:32,778 --> 00:23:35,251
Please take care of us next week.

409
00:24:45,431 --> 00:24:46,719
