411
00:24:48,882 --> 00:24:49,883
(The increased feeling)
I never thought

412
00:24:49,883 --> 00:24:51,924
I'd have this kind of feeling.

413
00:24:52,233 --> 00:24:53,189
(The distant feeling)
Minato-san,

414
00:24:53,213 --> 00:24:54,218
why did you come to the

415
00:24:54,227 --> 00:24:55,060
university as it suits you?

416
00:24:55,084 --> 00:24:56,462
What is it, Shin?

417
00:24:56,486 --> 00:24:57,997
Acting as if he dislikes me.

418
00:24:58,021 --> 00:24:58,863
Let's go.

419
